high_descs: Turn right, go straight to the counter to the left of the oven.
Take the small knife next to the apple from the counter.
Stay at the counter.
Cut the apple on the counter into pieces.
Turn left, go straight, turn right at the counter to the right of the sink.
Put the knife on the counter.
Go back to the counter to the left of the oven.
Take a piece of apple from the counter.
Turn left, go straight, stop at the sink.
Cook the piece of apple in the microwave. Take the apple from the microwave.
Turn to the right to face the sink.
Put the apple in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked piece of apple in a sink.

high_descs: turn right and walk over to the kitchen counter ahead
grab a butter knife off of the kitchen counter
look down a bit to see the apple on the kitchen counter better
slice up the apple on top of the kitchen counter with your butter knife in hand
turn left and walk over to the sink on the right side of the room
place the butter knife down on the kitchen counter to the right of the sink
move to the right a bit and face the kitchen counter again
grab a apple slice off of the kitchen counter
turn left and walk over to the microwave at the end of the room, don't turn to face it though
place the apple inside of the microwave, let it cook, then take it back out
move forwards a bit and face the kitchen sink on your right
place the apple slice down inside of the sink
anns.task_desc: place a cooked apple slice down inside of the kitchen sink

high_descs: Turn right and head to the counter to the left of the stove
Grab the knife that's on the counter
Look down at the counter
Cut the apple into three slices
Move slightly to the left
Place the knife on the counter
Move slightly to the right
Grab one of the apple slices
Turn left and stop at the microwave
Heat the apple in the microwave and then take it out
Turn to the sink on your right
Place the apple in the sink
anns.task_desc: Putting a apple slice in the sink

high_descs: Turn to the right and go to the counter straight ahead.
Pick up the butter knife that is on the counter.
Lower the knife down towards the apple.
Use the knife to cut the apple.
Turn to the left and go to the sink.
Stand the knife up on the right side of the sink.
Turn to the right and go back to the counter where the apple is.
Pick up a slice of the apple.
Turn to the left and go to the microwave.
Put the apple in the microwave and turn it on to cook., remove the apple from the microwave.
Turn to the right and go to the sink.
Put the apple in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked apple in the sink.
